OL,3,C1 in 7 adults in Wales cut spending to
OL,4,Cafford rent or mortgage bill
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, Shelter Cymru
OL,7,Fpolicy manager Lauren Caley explained
OL,8,Fthat the scale of the problem is "all
OL,9,Facross Wales" and "it's people that we
OL,10,Fall know that are facing this
OL,11,Ffinancial pressure".
OL,13,F"We know from our casework that people
OL,14,Fare turning the heating on less,
OL,15,Fthey're having much smaller-scale
OL,16,FChristmases, or potentially Christmas
OL,17,Fisn't happening at all," she said.
