OL,6,F"But that home is so, so essential -
OL,7,Fthat is a cost that people prioritise.
OL,8,FThey try to see where they can cut
OL,9,Fback in other areas and those niceties
OL,10,Fare the first to go, which is really
OL,11,Fdifficult as we move towards Christmas.
OL,13,F"There are hundreds and hundreds of
OL,14,Fchildren all across the country who
OL,15,Fwill be trying to celebrate in hotels,
OL,16,FB&Bs, hostels, and refuges all with
OL,17,Ftheir family trapped in one room."
