OL,6,F"We're tackling this through
OL,7,Fprevention, investing almost #240
OL,8,Fmillion this year in homelessness
OL,9,Fprevention and housing support. This
OL,10,Fincludes more than #204 million
OL,11,Fthrough the Housing Support Grant and
OL,12,Fschemes like Help to Stay Wales, which
OL,13,Fhelp people maintain their tenancies
OL,14,Fand mortgages before they reach crisis
OL,15,Fpoint.
OL,17,F"The Renting Homes (Wales) Act has
OL,18,Fgiven renters greater security and
OL,19,Fclearer rights while ensuring homes
OL,20,Fmeet decent standards.
